{"tid":1004430,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"Second In 傾得好愉快，跟住無聲氣","createTime":"2019-02-01T12:14:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-01T12:49:45.000Z","uid":188621,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"3e9e46a90f31b069d6cddb386afc657400a22bd2","tid":1004430,"uid":188621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T12:14:47.000Z","msg":"話說我上年年中我好瀟灑咁辭職讀個中大full-time master，算係做左幾年嘢，想透/回下氣，之後再搏過咁啦。<br />\n<br />\n其實個master可以hea讀，而且fulltime讀書無入息無咩安全感，所以又開始搵工，想著邊讀(part-time咁讀)邊賺錢啦。<br />\n<br />\n好啦，又要搵工，聖誕假send咗十幾封求職信，又LinkedIn又email咩都用，終於皇天不負有心人，有一份工可以見渦，當堂勁開心。<br />\n<br />\n話說個部門啊頭first in好鍾意我，雖然我牌面未必夠人勁，又無connection，又無父蔭，etc. 但是都被邀再次去公司second in. <br />\n<br />\nsecond in嗰日部門啊頭一開波就話&rdquo;今次係八揀二，你平常心得架啦&ldquo;，都係大老闆將我的CV由頭到尾問一次，無乜問technical嘢。<br />\n<br />\n最初都覺得應該OK掛，大家傾得咁開心，出來的時候又好大力咁握手，etc.，仲話過年前會有答覆，結果日復一日好似初戀咁捕住部電話，等啊等啊等，到今日都無電話啊～<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n看來，都係無咩希望架啦。<br />\n<br />\n再負面啲，遲啲讀完再搵工，變待業雙失點L算。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d57056d74d14c086dd523631ffa6687f894e7f61","tid":1004430,"uid":187072,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T12:16:54.000Z","msg":"仲有10個月先過年喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de089c055347d7cb21af697014810984484e112f","tid":1004430,"uid":84040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T12:19:25.000Z","msg":"1999<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f52c54a82eba591de76818d408825aee15edfc0","tid":1004430,"uid":188621,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"d57056d74d14c086dd523631ffa6687f894e7f61","tid":1004430,"uid":187072,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T12:16:54.000Z","msg":"仲有10個月先過年喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T12:19:37.000Z","msg":"哈哈哈，好風趣。"},{"